reated_at": "2022-04-27T14:46:54Z", "updated_at": "2022-04-28T06:23:51Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "OWNER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "## Windows10下载\r\n\r\n[Windows10 ISO]（https://www.microsoft.com/ja-jp/software-download/windows10iso）\r\n\r\n\r\n创建##引导媒体\r\n\r\n双击上面的网站上下载的ISO并将其安装。然后执行脚本如下。\r\n\r\nGPT-> MBR可能起作用。\r\n\r\n````bash\r\n$＃媒体格式\r\n$ diskutil Erasedisk MS-DOS“ Win10” GPT /DEV /DISK4\r\n传输文件以外的$＃sources/install.wim\r\n$ rsync -avh -progress -exclude = sources/install.wim/polumes/cccoma_x64fre_ja -jp_dv9 // dolumes/win10\r\n$＃sources/install.wim被划分并编写\r\n$ wimlib-imagex split/lumes/cccoma_x64fre_ja-jp_dv9/sources/install.wim/volumes/win10/sources/sources/install.swm 3200\r\n$＃ /dev /disk4安装\r\n$ diskutil unmountdisk /dev /disk4\r\n````````\r\n\r\n*将`/dev/disk4`更改为相应的外部USB媒体目录。 （您可以使用“ $ diskutil列表”检查当前连接的磁盘信息。）\r\n*如果未安装Wimlib，请执行并安装`$ BREW安装Wimlib`。\r\n\r\n执行后，它与普通的Windows安装过程相同。\r\n\r\n## Funning\r\n\r\n我记得使用DD命令很容易制作，但是什么时候变得如此复杂？\r\n\r\n似乎``install.wim''已超过4GB，超过了FAT32的上限（4GB）。\r\n\r\nSWM扩展名首次知道它似乎用于拆分WIM文件。", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/37/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/37/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}